---
description: Durable research memory rules
alwaysApply: true
---

Source-of-truth files:
- `RESEARCH.md`: concise current project constitution.
- `docs/TASKS.md`: task queue.
- `docs/DECISIONS.md`: PI-approved durable decisions.
- `docs/WHAT_WE_TRIED.md`: failed, rejected, and ambiguous attempts.
- `docs/DATA_SOURCES.md`: data provenance.
- `docs/IDENTIFICATION.md`: causal/descriptive logic.
- `docs/RESULTS_LOG.md`: traceable results.
- `docs/LITERATURE_MAP.md`: project-specific literature positioning.

Session logs are not source-of-truth. Consolidate important lessons into the durable files.
